data.title: Baron Sir Ferdinand von Mueller, 2 1/2 Pence, Australia, 13 Sep 1948
data.meta_description: First day cover, for 2 1/2 Pence (2 1/2d) Baron Sir Ferdinand von Mueller. Issued 13 September, 1948. Postmarked Melbourne, Victoria.
